{"title":"中国人民解放军三大纪律八项注意","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":10,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民解放军三大纪律八项注意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三大纪律："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）一切行动听指挥；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）不拿群众一针一线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）一切缴获要归公。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八项注意："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）说话和气；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）买卖公平；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）借东西要还；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）损坏东西要赔；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（五）不打人骂人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（六）不损坏庄稼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（七）不调戏妇女；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（八）不虐待俘虏。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}